### ====================================
### OWNERS - CRUD Completo
### ====================================

### Criar Owner
POST {{baseUrl}}/owner
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "João Silva",
  "telefone": "(81) 99999-9999"
}


### Buscar Owner por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/owner/{{ownerId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Atualizar Owner
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/owner/{{ownerId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "João Silva Atualizado",
  "telefone": "(81) 97777-7777"
}

### Atualizar apenas o nome
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/owner/{{ownerId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "João Pedro Silva"
}

### Atualizar apenas o telefone
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/owner/{{ownerId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "telefone": "(81) 96666-6666"
}

### Deletar Owner
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/owner/{{ownerId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

